text:
香港医管局员工阵线联盟昨日发起罢工投票，显示3123票支持、10票反对、23票弃权及8票无效，大比数通过发动罢工。

罢工共有9000余名医护联署，将于周一(3日)开始，提供非紧急服务的医护会率先进行罢工，若当局未有切实方案，提供紧急服务的医护会紧随进行罢工。

真是可耻！ ​
entext:
The Hong Kong Hospital Authority's Staff Front Coalition yesterday launched a strike vote, showing 3,123 votes in favour, 10 against, 23 abstentions and 8 invalidvotes.

The strike, which has more than 9,000 medical services, will begin on Monday ( 3 ) , with non-emergency services providing the first strike and, if there is no practical plan , the emergency services will follow .

What a shame!
